CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1951, pg. 32 reads: "Grads Of The College, Soldiers, Teachers - ...Right photo: Herbert M. Parrish and Irene Julia Cleveland earned the master of Education degree. Handley A. Hickey, previously a graduate of Wilberforce, finished his work for the Master of ...[de]gree.  All were Pitt commencement figures.  ...salutes all of them."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of University of Pittsburgh graduates, from left: Herbert M. Parrish, Irene Julia Cleveland, and Handley A. Hickey, standing in Syria Mosque, Oakland
